  </sponsors>
  <source>Heinrich-Heine University, Duesseldorf</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      We analyze the effects of combined intramuscular and intraarterial transplantation of BMCs in
      patients with PAD. BMCs were transplanted into the ischemic limb.

      After 2 and 13 months walking distance and perfusion indices were monitored.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
